    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Basically, you tried not to be outside if you didn't have to.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The fear of the German-- the Nazis, when they walked the streets, you just did not want to meet them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You did your shopping-- if you got your-- your-- your little ration cards, and you went round to get the shopping.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you basically stayed in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And you were waiting for the war to end.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
